Bacon Pancakes

I feel like this is very self explanatory! Cook some bacon, I prefer baking my bacon because it is SO much easier and all the pieces are consistent. Preheat oven to 385Â°F, arrange bacon on baking sheets with foil and bake to desired crispiness (16-22 minutes depending). Transfer bacon to paper towels to absorb any additional grease. Prepare pancake batter, toss bacon in batter to coat. Cook pancakes according to typical cooking instructions. Serve with powdered sugar and syrup and enjoy!
